snippet.title: [東方] Touhou - The Disappearing Of Gensokyo Ver 1.4 PV Trailer
snippet.description:
Trailer Music: youtube.com/watch?v=Y8j4oaYYKTg
Preview trailer for the Touhou Fangame "The Disappearing of Gensokyo" by MyACG, now available on Steam: http://store.steampowered.com/app/776490/__The_Disappearing_of_Gensokyo/
*The dev has granted permission for our channel to share their trailer*
UPDATE: Links to download the song is here folks: facebook.com/Touhou763/photos/1791815901106113 

NOTE: While the 60fps quality option is available for this upload, this video is NOT a 60fps game footage
The original video trailer was only a 30fps encoding of gameplay with persistent Frame Drop
The 60fps mode in this upload version is only meant to enhance the overall motion smoothness. Due to the severe frame irregularities occurring in the original video, the frame interpolation software unfortunately failed to achieve the usual buttery smooth 60fps interpolation
